author: Bruce Jenkins
title: Bad feelings precede Warriors-Clippers preseason matchup
text: LOS ANGELES — The NBA’s exhibition season has nothing to do with wins and losses. It’s more about territory. Like cats in a new neighborhood, certain teams and players need to make a point, nice and early, before the real schedule starts.
